g.text: Ian runs a research lab at UCL and is generally very busy. In addition to his research, he is also a lecturer to undergraduate students.As some of his lecture is too hard to understand for student. Therefore, he wish there is a platform that help him to prepare teaching material. MotivationsProvide the undergraduates with high quality and easy to follow teaching materialsGoalsGet high-quality material for assisting his lectureEnsure that the material difficulty is not too hard to understand.Pain pointsStudent cannot follow his lectureAnswering questions manually takes too long Cannot find alternate instructional materialNameProf. Ian PattersonAge51RoleProfessor at UCLI care about my undergrad students but cannot neglect my research Behaviours
